  "question": "A 55-year-old woman undergoes cholecystectomy for symptomatic gallstones. The final pathology returns one week after the operation showing gallbladder carcinoma. Which of the following statement(s) is/are true concerning this patient’s prognosis and management?\n\n![Image](/images/review_bank/37358425-Liver-Mcq-Surgery_98.jpeg)",
